        rdfs:comment        "PTK6 promotes cell cycle progression by phosphorylating and inactivating CDK inhibitor CDKN1B (p27) (Patel et al. 2015). PTK6 also negatively modulates CDKN1B expression via regulation of the activity of the FOXO3 (FOXO3A) transcription factor (Chan and Nimnual 2010)." ;
